reviewText: I got this dvd at a time when I was down and needed a pick me up. This dvd was hilarious and full of wisdom. Even for the person that is not religious, spiritual, whatever, it is still a great dvd to have.

I like Jesse Duplantis.  This is a great series to encourage you in your faith, as well as remind you to laugh along the way.  God has a sense of humor, so why shouldn't we?  Can't wait to watch all of it...
